## 11 Some Conclusions and Predictions

So, our analysis of the available data strongly suggests that the downward trend in buyout returns is set to continue, but let us keep this conclusion in context. First, I strongly suspect that the downward trend is not a straight line, as suggested by the graphing techniques we have

