Hopefully having read this far you will have a good idea of what buyout and venture capital are, what drives their returns, and what to look for when selecting funds in which to invest. You have also had a chance to consider the historic returns of each asset class, arranged by geography, and to take a look at how these might be influenced not just by transitory outside factors such as bubbles and market conditions but also to discern the workings of more lasting trends.

